flowchart TD
    A[Admin opens one content list page] --> B{Choose area}
    B -->|Module| C[Module CRUD]
    B -->|Lesson| D[Lesson CRUD]
    B -->|E-Book| E[Ebook CRUD]
    B -->|Video Lecture| F[Course CRUD]

    C --> G[Open create or edit form]
    D --> G
    E --> G
    F --> G

    G --> H[Validate form data]
    H --> I{Valid?}
    I -->|No| J[Show validation errors]
    I -->|Yes| K[Save record]
    K --> L[Redirect back to list with flash success]

    M[Delete action] --> N[Show confirmation dialog]
    N --> O{Confirmed?}
    O -->|No| P[Cancel delete]
    O -->|Yes| Q[Check dependency rules]
    Q --> R{Allowed?}
    R -->|No| S[Show error]
    R -->|Yes| T[Delete record and return to list]

    U[Upload constraints] --> V[File size max 10 MB]
    U --> W[Module Lesson and Ebook use multi-tier access]
    U --> X[Lesson tiers must be subset of parent module tiers]
